Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.125
Let's view the available updates on our CentOS server.

00:00:04.125 --> 00:00:07.425
To view available updates in CentOS type

00:00:07.425 --> 00:00:15.430
"Sudo" for elevated privileges, "Yum," and "Check-update."

00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:19.810
You'll be asked to enter your credentials again.

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:28.749
Now, you can see all the updates that are available for your install packages.

